snippet.title: Justice For JOHNNY DEPP! Why He Must Win Against Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Justice for Johnny Depp is so important but let's talk about why he must win against Amber Heard and The Sun.

With me is Truthy McGoo, another youtube creator covering the case, so join us.

Johnny Depp is innocent and Amber Heard must be held accountable for what she has done.
